<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Bia sunglawi hla aw dawh te bang lung-rethei mi sin a phan, lungder mi
 le thaba mi cu hnangam dinhnak a pek hna.

[C1]
   Hna-ngamnak tling cu na pek lai, Nangmah an zummi cu, Nangmah kha an
   bochan ca, (an bochan ca) Nangmah kha an bochan ca. (nangmah, nangmah kha
   an bochan ca, bochan ca)

[V2]
 Bia sunglawi nih a kan hnemh tawn, tihnung zan caan phanh tikah, Kan
 kalnak kha a ceuter, a dawtnak aw thlum cu kan theih.

[C2]
   Hna-ngamnak tling cu na pek lai, Nangmah an zummi cu, Nangmah kha an
   bochan ca, (an bochan ca) Nangmah kha an bochan ca. (nangmah, nangmah kha
   an bochan ca, bochan ca)

[V3]
 Bia sunglawi biakam thiang a si, Vancungmi ceunak hmun in, Thlarau nih
 lungchung ah a phuan, zandai thlavang ceu tangah.

[C3]
   Hna-ngamnak tling cu na pek lai, Nangmah an zummi cu, Nangmah kha an
   bochan ca, (an bochan ca) Nangmah kha an bochan ca. (nangmah, nangmah kha
   an bochan ca, bochan ca)

[V4]
 Bia sunglawi a kan cawisangtu, Vawlei rumnak in sung deuh Zungzal
 nunnak dong lo cerhti, Dong lo dawtnak hram a si.

[C4]
   Hna-ngamnak tling cu na pek lai, Nangmah an zummi cu, Nangmah kha an
   bochan ca, (an bochan ca) Nangmah kha an bochan ca. (nangmah, nangmah kha
   an bochan ca, bochan ca)</lyrics>
<key>A</key>
<title>HNANGAMNAK TLING CH472</title>
<hymn_number>472</hymn_number>
</song>